; Ship the client runtime assets with the `fennec` package so apps can reference
; them instead of vendoring their own: the preact entry (built into the static
; React/ReactDOM globals bundle) and the require-shim banner that maps the app
; bundle's react externals to those globals.
(install
 (section share)
 (package fennec)
 (files
  preact_entry.mjs
  require_shim.js))
